Contained within this torrent are all of the Grimm Fairy Tale one shots, minis, and the main series itself.  The collection is complete and up to date as of the day of posting. However, be aware that the series itself is still ongoing and the current mini(Beyond Wonderland) is only half complete.  If this torrent receives enough interest, I will update as new books are scanned.

The covers to the comics are quite sensationalistic, often depicting girls in very risque poses.  This might lead you to expect some hentai-like action.  If that's what you are looking for, move along; there's nothing to see here.  While the books contain many adult scenarios, nothing is shown past a PG13 degree of sexual activity.  Graphic violence(yay!) reigns here.  In the most basic sense, this is a horror anthology with female protagonists starring in morality plays based on fairy tales.  Barring perhaps Fables and Hellblazer, this is probably the best written ongoing horror series being published today.

I've also included folder full of alternate covers, for those of you who get excited about such things.
